data.name: Toyota Supra
data.description:
Experience the hype everyone is talking about. Take this toyota supra out and have a feel for yourself the reborn japanese legend. You are sure to enjoy the car regardless of the weather conditions. This is a car you can enjoy just staring at its beauty and also enjoy experiencing the power this engine offers.
Please note: this car is equipped with a security device that collects driving data. This includes vehicle location, and may include other driving data such as mileage, driving behaviour, and time driven. This information may be shared with third parties for vehicle recovery or insurance purposes. By booking this vehicle you consent to the use of the device.
